      <div class="prose max-w-3xl text-[var(--color-text-body)]">
        <p>Last updated: 31 March 2026</p>

        <h2>1. Services</h2>
        <p>ChinaWebFoundry provides WordPress development, hosting, migration, and related digital services for the Chinese market. The specific scope of services is defined in individual project agreements.</p>

        <h2>2. Use of this website</h2>
        <p>You may use this website for lawful purposes only. You must not use this website in any way that causes or may cause damage to the website or impairs its availability.</p>

        <h2>3. Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and images, is the property of ChinaWebFoundry unless otherwise stated. You may not reproduce, distribute, or modify any content without our written permission.</p>

        <h2>4. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>ChinaWebFoundry shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of this website or our services, except where required by applicable law.</p>

